examples.en: Nocturnal animals are active at night.
Rebecca paid a nocturnal visit to the flat.
Nocturnal plants have flowers that open at night and close by day.
The leaves assumed their nocturnal dependent position.
He bought a new telescope so he could pursue his favorite nocturnal hobby of astronomy.
A nocturnal visitant that must have been the shade of his late brother, crying out for vengeance against his murderers.
